languages.text: "Не надо мне никакой награды, миленьк{mf|ий|ая} госпо{mf|дин|жа}! Я хочу домой вернуться!" {n}Женщина опускает голову и сжимает пальцы на кружеве платья. Ее дыхание сбивается от беззвучных рыданий.{/n}

"But I don't want no reward, {mf|m'lord|m'lady}! I want to get back home!" {n}The woman hangs her head and clutches the lace frills on her dress. Her breathing stutters as she is racked with silent sobs.{/n}

languages.text: “可我不想要什么奖励，大人！我只想回家！”{n}年轻女人低下了头，紧紧抓住裙子上的花边。她无声地抽泣着，呼吸断断续续。{/n}
languages.original_text: "But I don't want no reward, {mf|m'lord|m'lady}! I want to get back home!" {n}The woman hangs her head and clutches the lace frills on her dress. Her breathing stutters as she is racked with silent sobs.{/n}

traits.locale_text: “可我不想要什么奖励，大人！我只想回家，只想活着回去！”{n}年轻女人低下了头，紧紧抓住裙子上的花边。她无声地抽泣着，呼吸断断续续。{/n}

languages.text: 「でも、報酬なんていらないよ、ありがたき方！私は家に帰りたいんだ！」{n}女性はうなだれ、ドレスのレースのフリルをぎゅっと握りしめた。彼女は声を上げることもできずにすすり泣き、呼吸が途切れがちになる。{/n}

traits.locale_text: 「でも、報酬なんていらないよ、ありがたき方！私は家に帰りたいんだ。ちゃんと生きて！」{n}女性はうなだれ、ドレスのレースのフリルをぎゅっと握りしめた。彼女は声を上げることもできずにすすり泣き、呼吸が途切れがちになる。{/n}

languages.text: «¡Pero es que no quiero recompensa, {mf|milord|milady}! ¡Lo que quiero es volver a mi casa!». {n}La mujer agacha la cabeza y se agarra los volantes de encaje del vestido. Solloza en silencio con la respiración entrecortada.{/n}
languages.original_text: "But I don't want no reward, {mf|m'lord|m'lady}! I want to get back home!" {n}The woman hangs her head and clutches the lace frills on her dress. Her breathing stutters as she is racked with silent sobs.{/n}

traits.locale_text: «¡Pero es que no quiero recompensa, {mf|milord|milady}! Lo que quiero es volver a mi casa. ¡Viva!». {n}La mujer agacha la cabeza y se agarra los volantes de encaje del vestido. Solloza en silencio con la respiración entrecortada.{/n}

languages.text: "İyi de ben ödül filan istemiyorum {mf|lordum|leydim}! Eve döneyim istiyorum!" {n}Kadın, başını öne eğip elbisesinin dantel fırfırlarını sımsıkı kavrıyor. Hırıltılı nefesi, sessiz hıçkırıklarıyla kesiliyor.{/n}
languages.original_text: "But I don't want no reward, {mf|m'lord|m'lady}! I want to get back home!" {n}The woman hangs her head and clutches the lace frills on her dress. Her breathing stutters as she is racked with silent sobs.{/n}

traits.locale_text: "İyi de ben ödül filan istemiyorum {mf|lordum|leydim}! Ben evime sağ salim döneyim istiyorum! {n}Kadın, başını önüne eğip elbisesinin dantel fırfırlarını sımsıkı kavrıyor. Hırıltılı nefesi, sessiz hıçkırıklarıyla kesiliyor.{/n}

languages.text: « Mais je ne veux pas de récompense, {mf|monseigneur|ma dame} ! Je veux juste rentrer chez moi ! » {n}La femme incline la tête en serrant les volants en dentelle de sa robe. Sa respiration est saccadée par des sanglots muets.{/n}
languages.original_text: "But I don't want no reward, {mf|m'lord|m'lady}! I want to get back home!" {n}The woman hangs her head and clutches the lace frills on her dress. Her breathing stutters as she is racked with silent sobs.{/n}

traits.locale_text: « Mais je ne veux pas de récompense, {mf|monseigneur|ma dame} ! Je veux juste rentrer chez moi. Vivante ! » {n}La femme incline la tête en serrant les volants en dentelle de sa robe. Sa respiration est saccadée par des sanglots muets.{/n}

languages.text: "Aber ich will gar keine Belohnung, {mf|Herr|Herrin}! Ich will nach Hause!" {n}Die Frau lässt den Kopf hängen und umklammert die Spitzenrüschen an ihrem Kleid. Sie atmet stockend und wird von geräuschlosem Schluchzen geschüttelt.{/n}
